### StaqFinance API — Requests de teste
### Visual Studio: clique em "Send Request" acima de cada requisição
### Documentação completa: src/Api/docs/API.md

@baseUrl = https://localhost:7275

### Variáveis preenchidas após login (copie os valores das respostas)
@accessToken = SEU_ACCESS_TOKEN_AQUI
@refreshToken = SEU_REFRESH_TOKEN_AQUI

# =============================================================================
# HEALTH
# =============================================================================

### [1] Health check da API
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/health

###

### [2] Health check do banco de dados
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/health/db

###

# =============================================================================
# AUTH — Register
# =============================================================================

### [3] Cadastrar novo usuário (201 Created)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "joao@example.com",
  "password": "Abc12345",
  "displayName": "João Silva",
  "workspaceName": "Meu Orçamento"
}

###

### [4] Cadastrar com e-mail duplicado (409 Conflict)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "joao@example.com",
  "password": "Abc12345",
  "displayName": "João Silva 2",
  "workspaceName": "Outro Workspace"
}

###

### [5] Cadastrar com senha fraca (400 Bad Request)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "teste@example.com",
  "password": "123",
  "displayName": "Teste",
  "workspaceName": "Workspace Teste"
}

###

# =============================================================================
# AUTH — Login
# =============================================================================

### [6] Login com sucesso (200 OK) — copie accessToken e refreshToken
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "joao@example.com",
  "password": "Abc12345"
}

###

### [7] Login com senha errada (401 Unauthorized)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "joao@example.com",
  "password": "SenhaErrada1"
}

###

### [8] Login com e-mail inexistente (401 Unauthorized)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "naocadastrado@example.com",
  "password": "Abc12345"
}

###

# =============================================================================
# AUTH — Refresh token
# =============================================================================

### [9] Renovar tokens (200 OK) — preencha @refreshToken acima
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/refresh
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "token": "{{refreshToken}}"
}

###

### [10] Refresh com token inválido (401 Unauthorized)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/refresh
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "token": "token-invalido"
}

###

# =============================================================================
# ME
# =============================================================================

### [11] Obter dados do usuário autenticado (200 OK) — preencha @accessToken acima
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/me
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

###

### [12] Obter dados sem token (401 Unauthorized)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/me

###

# =============================================================================
# WORKSPACE — Ping (requer usuário membro do workspace)
# =============================================================================

### [13] Ping no workspace (200 OK) — substitua o slug pelo gerado no register
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/workspaces/meu-orcamento/_ping
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

###

### [14] Ping em workspace inexistente (404)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/workspaces/nao-existe/_ping
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

###
